<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FlightBooker - Book Your Flight</title>

</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>FlightBooker</h1>
        <p>Book your flights online easily</p>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome to FlightBooker</h2>
        <p>At FlightBooker you can easily search and book flights to various destinations. We offer flights in Economy and Business Class, with different meal options to make your trip as pleasant as possible.</p>


        <a class="home-flight" asp-area="" asp-controller="FlightSearch" asp-action="Index">Search a flight</a>
        <h2 id="destinations">Our Destinations</h2>
        <div class="destinations">
            <div class="destination" style="background-image: url('../images/7.jpg');">
                <div class="banner-overlay">
                    <h3>Tokyo</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination" style="background-image: url('../images/2.jpg');">
                <div class="banner-overlay">
                    <h3>Cape Town</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination" style="background-image: url('../images/6.jpg');">
                <div class="banner-overlay">
                    <h3>Singapore</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination" style="background-image: url('../images/3.jpg');">
                <div class="banner-overlay">
                    <h3>London</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination" style="background-image: url('../images/4.jpg');">
                <div class="banner-overlay">
                    <h3>New York</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination" style="background-image: url('../images/1.jpg');">
                <div class="banner-overlay">
                    <h3>Dubai</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="destination" style="background-image: url('../images/5.jpg');">
                <div class="banner-overlay">
                    <h3>Sydney</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="meals">Meal Options</h2>
        <div class="meal-options">
            <h3>We offer the following meal options:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Standard:</strong> Grilled chicken with potatoes</li>
                <li><strong>Vegetarian:</strong> Vegetable risotto</li>
                <li><strong>Vegan:</strong> Lentil curry</li>
                <li><strong>Halal:</strong> Lamb with rice</li>
                <li><strong>Kosher:</strong> Appetizer, main course and dessert according to Jewish rules</li>
                <li><strong>Gluten-free:</strong> Chicken fillet with vegetables</li>
                <li><strong>Locally Inspired:</strong> For example sushi for flights to Tokyo</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You can indicate your meal choice during booking or change it later via your account.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="policy">Booking Policy</h2>
        <div class="booking-policy">
            <h3>Important information about bookings:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Free cancellation up to 7 days before departure</li>
                <li>Choice of Economy and Business Class</li>
                <li>Create an account to manage your bookings</li>
                <li>Easily change your meal preferences or cancel your booking via your account</li>
            </ul>
        </div>



    </div>

</body>
</html>